Enclosing class:
WrapperOpenDomino
public static class WrapperOpenDomino.OpenObject
extends com.ibm.jscript.types.GeneratedWrapperObject

The OpenObject is base wrapper for the Java classes that defines their names, method maps and unlying Java classes. These objects are registered with the WrapperFactory with integer indexes so that the SSJS interpretter can find the appropriate wrapper for Java objects at runtime.
